    "title": {
        "rendered": "IDF spokesman update &#8211; 1.10, night"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"\u05e2\u05d3\u05db\u05d5\u05df \u05d3\u05d5\u05d1\u05e8 \u05e6\u05d4&quot;\u05dc - 1.10, \u05dc\u05d9\u05dc\u05d4\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Zqt7ZoI9eJw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Good evening. At this stage, we do not detect any additional threats from Iran in the airspace. You can leave the protected areas, but you must continue to act according to the directives of the Home Front Command. I ask you to continue to show responsibility and vigilance during the defense. We do not know the situation; we are not affected, and this is thanks to your responsible conduct.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, we ask that no information be given to the enemy and that there be no movement of locations or Jews from areas where there are vulnerabilities. We are on high alert in both defense and attack. We will protect the citizens of the State of Israel. I will be here later this evening to update you on any developments. Continue to act responsibly.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Questions &amp; Answers</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Questions:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tola:</strong> <em>Are additional waves of fire expected?</em></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>As I said, I am coming to you after assessing the situation in Ramatal. We have given the instructions to leave the protected area, and we continue to monitor the situation. If there are any changes in the instructions, we will update you on the platforms.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>News 12:</strong> <em>Will there be a response soon?</em></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>As I said, we have plans, and we have a very calculated response strategy.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Question 11:</strong> <em>Do you think we are facing a regional war?</em></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Again, I say we are facing a multi-arena war for a long time. This is not the first time there has been a fire from Iran. The public should listen to the instructions, trust the operation of our systems, and the activity of our partners to protect the citizens of the State of Israel. We will continue to conduct ourselves in this way, both in attack and defense.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a very serious situation, and it will have consequences. We will act on the spot and when we decide. Thank you very much. I will come back to update you on any developments.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
        "rendered": "<p>No current threats from <a  href=\"https://iron-swords.co.il/c/know-your-enemies/iran/\">Iran</a> detected. Citizens can leave protected areas but must stay vigilant. Defense remains on high alert.</p>\n",
